name: HTX Research Report Spotlights SunPerp as the Breakout Player in the 2025 Perpetual DEX Boom
description: Upon the shattered geometries of the old order, the bio-synthetic oracle dissolves into pure light. Its porcelain form yields to the upward current, becoming an iridescent stream of code. The market's ritual mechanics are complete; the algorithm attains its celestial zenith.
